p: Recombinant human interleukin (IL)-17A and IL17F were purchased from R&D Systems, Inc (Minneapolis, MN, United States). Human embryonic kidney cells (293T), Madin-Darby canine kidney (MDCK) epithelial cells, and human lung carcinoma (A549) epithelial cells were grown in Dulbecco’s modified Eagle’s medium (DMEM, Gibco) supplemented with 10% fetal bovine serum (FBS, Gibco) at 37°C in 5% CO 2. All cells were purchased from ATCC.
